data.description: WOW! WHAT A DEAL! Welcome to 371 Rogers ct, a splendid 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom oasis in the heart of Calimesa! This Home features a remodeled kitchen and airy living space, where the beautiful flooring flows seamlessly throughout. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the fully renovated kitchen, boasting modern elegance with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and custom cabinetry. Escape to your private retreat in the backyard, where a sparkling POOL awaits your relaxation. This home is not only a visual delight but also an eco-friendly haven with its solar system, ensuring energy efficiency and cost savings. Dont Forget the Convenience of having your own Electric Vehicle Charger fully installed. Embrace sustainable living while enjoying the comfort of your stylish residence. For those with recreational vehicles or a boat, the possibility of RV parking adds an extra layer of convenience. No need to worry about extra storage fees. Nestled in the City of Calimesa, this property is a rare find with no HOA or Mello Roos tax, offering the freedom to enjoy your home without additional financial burdens. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional residence your own!
